      <div class="project-card fade-up">
        <span class="project-num">001</span>
        <div class="project-title">Plateforme SaaS Analytics</div>
        <p class="project-desc">Dashboard temps réel pour l'analyse de données métier. Architecture micro-services, visualisations D3.js, authentification JWT et API REST complète.</p>
        <div class="skill-tags project-tags">
          <span class="tag">React</span>
          <span class="tag">Node.js</span>
          <span class="tag">PostgreSQL</span>
        </div>
