        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="project-card fade-up">
        <span class="project-num">002</span>
        <div class="project-title">API Gateway Microservices</div>
        <p class="project-desc">Passerelle API centralisant l'authentification, le rate limiting et le routage pour une architecture distribuée de 5 services indépendants.</p>
        <div class="skill-tags project-tags">
          <span class="tag">Python</span>
          <span class="tag">FastAPI</span>
          <span class="tag">Docker</span>
        </div>
        <div class="project-links">
          <a class="project-link" href="#">GitHub →</a>
          <a class="project-link" href="#">Documentation →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="project-card fade-up">
        <span class="project-num">003</span>
        <div class="project-title">App Mobile E-Commerce</div>
        <p class="project-desc">Application mobile cross-platform avec paiement Stripe, gestion d'inventaire en temps réel et notifications push. 2000+ utilisateurs actifs.</p>
        <div class="skill-tags project-tags">
          <span class="tag">React Native</span>
          <span class="tag">Firebase</span>
          <span class="tag">Stripe</span>
        </div>
        <div class="project-links">
          <a class="project-link" href="#">GitHub →</a>
          <a class="project-link" href="#">App Store →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
